text.tspan: People seeking help from experts need a way to be able to confidently find a respective expert and ask questions without
adding any more complication to the problem(s). They need a solution from someone reputable in a quick and seamless
manner. This will be known to be true when an expert is shown to receive or build reputation and respect through the number
Create a mobile app (tablet or smartphone) that allows users to be able to search categories of experts
Allow person to request assistance from expert
Allow person to rate the expert or mark problem as solved/unsolved
